{"tid":2092632,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"依本國際文宣好快就會被打壓。","createTime":"2020-07-03T10:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T06:29:07.000Z","uid":107092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71b23a9cede88c745c2fed389e6d918d61385268","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>背景</ins></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PmcZaHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPmcZaHs.png&h=fa9aae01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n作品嘅創作背景係回應 The Wyng Media Award(WMA)，<br />\n主要係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想推動公眾對香港社會議題嘅關注（包括社運）。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而2018-2019年WMA大師攝影奬題目就係「機遇」，<br />\n所以團隊就重組機遇同香港嘅關係。<br />\n為咗令外國朋友知道香港情況，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成本書都有中英對照。</strong></span><br />\n（本書嘅出版社有作品<span style=\"color: red;\">被外國圖書館收錄，</span>而要面向世界就要<span style=\"color: red;\">走入當地。</span>）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>究竟同文宣有咩關係？</ins></strong></span><br />\n依本「書」有多個展覽項目，<br />\n而裝住「展覽項目」嘅內頁係有一連三版嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Glossary詞𢑥，</span></strong><br />\n分別<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為香港關鍵字作中英對照解釋，</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>例如黑警、陳彥霖、香城Online、721元朗、港豬、爆眼少女等等等等，</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算冇關注香港嘅外國人都能快速認識。<br />\n<br />\n本書唔單止係講反送中運動，<br />\n仲帶大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>搞清香港歷史及社會脈絡。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPciroO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPciroO.png&h=0beed648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一部分「一個國情 兩種演繹」，<br />\n入面就講一個概念之下政權同民間嘅演繹有咩分別，<br />\n例如<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政權話一國兩制，民間只會見到一國1.5制；</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政權話要有自由行，民間就想要自由閪。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本書仲有講<span style=\"color: red;\">香港教育制度，</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">學生點衡量罷課同機會成本</span>等等嘅貼地議題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本書仲有好多貼地議題，<br />\n唔講太多，大家自己睇片。<br />\n<br />\n中英對照之下，<br />\n外國人能夠了解香港現實係幾腐敗亦更了解運動起因，<br />\n香港人都能夠透過本書更清楚香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>依本書真係值得大家擁有，<br />\n請支持香港文化產業，<br />\n依類咁用心嘅創作，好快就會被打壓。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好嫌片長，睇完導讀就知道背後創作團隊付出幾多。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xN9BioO-s1g&amp;list=PLdV6ZvU5ps_ltjJce7SNZNo2rffUBMSO0&amp;index=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxN9BioO-s1g%26list%3DPLdV6ZvU5ps_ltjJce7SNZNo2rffUBMSO0%26index%3D3&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=58eae4e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xN9BioO-s1g&amp;list=PLdV6ZvU5ps_ltjJce7SNZNo2rffUBMSO0&amp;index=3</a>"},{"pid":"7cfc0f404842529c90c97b9eaed1cb24316db0d8","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:07:45.000Z","msg":"依本嘢真係好值得大家睇 / 比外國朋友認識香港，<br />\n成日話反送中只係導火線，<br />\n本書就帶大家回顧晒過往社會嘅不堪。<br />\n<br />\n購買《機遇之後：回應WMA 2018/19 主題「機遇」》After Opportunity: A response to WMA 2018/19 theme &lsquo;Opportunuty&rsquo;：<br />\n<a href=\"http://mossesbooks.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmossesbooks.hk%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=8cba4d42\" target=\"_blank\">http://mossesbooks.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n門市發售地點：<br />\nBOOK B&mdash;Shop 111, The Mills, 45 Pak Tin Par Street, Tsuen Wan<br />\nMOSSES&mdash;14 St. Francis Street, Wan Chai, Hong Kong"},{"pid":"c44ce0405fc47f28c176e5c779c038a572571a09","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"另外佢地有展覽：<br />\n機遇之後&mdash;&mdash;重讀．回應 After Opportunity-Rereading and Responding Exhibition】⁣<br />\n⁣<br />\n「機遇之後&mdash;&mdash;重讀．回應」是一場以「後設」為概念的「紙上展覽」，將藝術作品、社會時事透過書籍設計及編輯的方式進行詮釋，讓參觀者在觀展過程中建立個人對於出版的思考和想像。展覽透過七本裝幀、選紙、開本各異的攝影集，並延伸出三本關於香港社會現況的書誌，重新想像「機遇」的意義，邀請觀眾以俯瞰的視野，重讀這20年來香港與「機遇」之間複雜難解的關係。<br />\n<br />\n在重讀以後，展覽亦邀請觀眾寫下個人的回應。所有回應將在未來組合成書，成為另一本在「借來的空間；借來的時間」中共同閱讀、共同思考、共同書寫的紀錄。在未來的日子，冀於其他場合重現，引發更大的迴響。<br />\n<br />\n2.7-23.7.2020 回歸過後，一同以書本回應時代。<br />\n<br />\n展覽詳情：⁣<br />\n[url]⁣<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZoBoWh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZoBoWh&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=079d411b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZoBoWh</a>  ⁣[/url]<br />\n⁣由於展覽需登記入場，請於以下連結登記：⁣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.hk/e/-after-opportunity-rereading-and-responding-registration-109779509468⁣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eventbrite.hk%2Fe%2F-after-opportunity-rereading-and-responding-registration-109779509468%E2%81%A3&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=e08ce577\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eventbrite.hk/e/-after-opportunity-rereading-and-responding-registration-109779509468⁣</a>"},{"pid":"2dd239298ac5e2fb7a65851e3a1a4e326a158f6a","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:08:41.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n[1] 本土創作的辛酸<br />\n榮光創作團隊DGX專訪： 被忽視的軟實力，蝕錢都堅持創作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/axKFLeU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/axKFLeU</a><br />\n<br />\n[2]黃圈並非理性消費<br />\n【長文】震驚中共！黃色經濟圈重點在於培育本土意識！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034646\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034646</a><br />\n<br />\n[3]另一本高質文宣<br />\n原來有咁高質嘅出版文宣，仲要被打壓緊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/axerrFU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/axerrFU</a>"},{"pid":"0ef07cc6387dd40a9182acac93c5a0a43e614143","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:10:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c435bc6372af413f3b6d827a41c3596847ad3263","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbae9545af1ccecbaa459776b2d0526f0cae4091","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a2063f8a376177dc67f3e5982d16979d2ebee7","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ee9e38a7a84da7fbd01c4304373adab149f073","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd24408a53787385b76d008b0d1807bafff9eed2","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"求幫推"},{"pid":"a7dc445a62793d81e7214ea29df83288ff3a259d","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4804c476f25438981b41f1b584db58837b610e1d","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d9e69e14c110038182149b6b303b7540f6270b","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e623377e38e47ff9c276d322ab3886753418507","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7863e6e4cfe1a31dabb4156f4f263529e507038","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce88f91d22bfad83637072bd09d0094564d1919","tid":2092632,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e685f021a87bc7d4398311ff570a7f5d996fc203","tid":2092632,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"完全冇人理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb84424c7f89104bd98021a8d5d26b3f4b3cec0","tid":2092632,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"搬去創意台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068a356daceb1c41c503bba0b8a483ff21a626f3","tid":2092632,"uid":332713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"f2a7b9efb9b60aff3ca99d595ff95f21f99852fb","tid":2092632,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推"},{"pid":"738006f8c666304e6e3d87fcec1088399dc1c03b","tid":2092632,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"哇屌 仲用SF送咁高危<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d737f62b4624c94bf1f72636071f7f21286aa3","tid":2092632,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920f9b9e5b26cf5656a68752864af9cf388b83c2","tid":2092632,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:29:07.000Z","msg":": 我地不如講下本土文化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n: <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n: 香港展覽好正架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}